snippet.title: Zenith's Call - Necromancer Gameplay (Alpha MMO)
snippet.description:
An early look at a battle encounter in the alpha MMO, Zenith's Call.
Shown is a Lv. 1 Necromancer.  If you're interested in following Zenith's Call, you can follow us at https://www.zenithscall.com/ or our Discord: https://discord.gg/GwZCUUd
